            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-forest-dark mb-2">Beat Procrastination</h3>
            <p class="font-hand text-ink-light leading-relaxed text-sm">David figured out why new systems always collapse around week three. ThinkDone is designed for the days you don't feel like it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-product-card mt-reveal">
            <div class="mt-product-icon" style="background: rgba(42,157,143,0.1);">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #2a9d8f" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-forest-dark mb-2">Stop Overcommitting</h3>
            <p class="font-hand text-ink-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Maya learned to stop saying yes to everything. ThinkDone's "day ends here" line shows you exactly how much fits &mdash; before you overpromise.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-product-card mt-reveal">
            <div class="mt-product-icon" style="background: rgba(231,111,81,0.1);">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #e76f51" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-forest-dark mb-2">Skip the App Circus</h3>
            <p class="font-hand text-ink-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Rachel tried every planner and to-do app on the market. ThinkDone is deliberately simple &mdash; one list, no setup, nothing to configure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-product-card mt-reveal">
            <div class="mt-product-icon" style="background: rgba(74,111,165,0.1);">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #4a6fa5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-forest-dark mb-2">Never Forget Again</h3>
            <p class="font-hand text-ink-light leading-relaxed text-sm">James kept dropping commitments &mdash; birthdays, follow-ups, promises. ThinkDone's memory catches everything so nothing slips through.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-product-card mt-reveal">
            <div class="mt-product-icon" style="background: rgba(78,205,196,0.1);">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #4ecdc4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-forest-dark mb-2">Let the Computer Do It</h3>
            <p class="font-hand text-ink-light leading-relaxed text-sm">Kai believes if you're manually copying things between calendars and apps, something is broken. ThinkDone connects the dots for you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê TESTIMONIAL / TEAM QUOTE ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê -->
    <section class="mt-section bg-paper mt-graph-bg">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center mt-reveal">
        <blockquote class="mt-team-quote">
          <p class="font-display italic text-3xl md:text-4xl text-ink-light leading-snug mb-8">
            We kept forgetting things, missing deadlines, and feeling behind. So we built the tool we all wished we'd had &mdash; one that remembers everything and tells you what to do next.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
        <div class="mt-team-avatars">
          {sorted.map(author => (
            <img src={imgUrl(author.data.avatar, { w: 80, h: 80, fit: 'crop' })} width="40" height="40" alt={author.data.name} class="mt-team-tiny-avatar" />
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="font-ui text-sm text-ink-muted mt-4">The ThinkDone Team</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê PRICING ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê -->
    <section id="pricing" class="mt-section bg-warm">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-14 mt-reveal">
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-forest-dark mb-4">
            Simple pricing. Serious clarity.
          </h2>
          <p class="font-hand text-xl text-ink-muted">
            Start small or go all in. Every plan includes your AI planning dashboard.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-price-grid">
          <!-- STARTER -->
          <div class="mt-price-card mt-reveal">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-forest-dark mb-2">Starter</h3>
            <div class="mb-2">
              <span class="font-display font-bold text-5xl text-forest-dark">$5</span>
              <span class="font-ui text-ink-muted">/month</span>
            </div>
            <p class="font-hand text-ink-muted mb-6">Pay-as-you-go AI. Perfect for trying it out.</p>
            <ul class="mt-price-features">
              <li><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-success shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg><span>Interactive task dashboard</span></li>
              <li><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-success shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg><span>AI planning meetings (pay per use)</span></li>
              <li><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-success shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg><span>Basic memory system</span></li>
